<p>Tincture is a pure Lean library with minimal dependencies. No native code or special build scripts are required.</p>

<h3>Requirements</h3>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://lean-lang.org/">Lean 4</a> (v4.26.0+)</li>
  <li>Lake (included with Lean)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Lakefile Configuration</h3>

<p>Add Tincture to your <code>lakefile.lean</code>:</p>

<pre><code class="language-lean">require tincture from git "https://github.com/nathanial/tincture" @ "v0.0.1"</code></pre>

<h3>Building</h3>

<pre><code class="language-bash"># Build the library
lake build

# Run tests
lake test</code></pre>

<h3>Dependencies</h3>

<p>Tincture has minimal dependencies:</p>

