<h3>Quick Verification</h3>

<p>After adding Tincture to your project, verify it works:</p>

<pre><code class="language-lean">import Tincture

open Tincture (Color)

-- Should compile successfully
def testColor : Color :=
  Color.lerp Color.red Color.blue 0.5</code></pre>

